# UI and Content Quality

Arabic-first public pages must be:
- clear
- institutional
- not hype-driven
- not vague
- not overclaiming AI autonomy

Avoid:
- "AI replaces your team"
- "fully automated audit"
- "guaranteed compliance"
- generic SaaS language
- empty enterprise buzzwords

Preferred language:
- private institutional intelligence
- governed AI
- evidence-linked workflows
- human review
- controlled pilots
- auditability
- traceability
- operational proof

For UI changes:
- preserve accessibility
- avoid layout regressions
- keep bilingual consistency where relevant
- avoid fake links or inactive product claims
